nt was attended by more than 12000 plumbers. Mahotsav 2019 saw active participation from 27 Organisations. Plumbing Skills Mahotsav also showcased range of advanced products, mega plumbers meets, educational seminars and job placement workshops by international & domestic brands likeHindware, Bathline, National Science Foundation (NSF), Watertec, Viega, Jain Plumbing, Acquaviva, Ori-Plast, Hepco, Rothenberger, Kitec, Parryware, Xylem, Ashirvad, Products Unlimited, Kranti Meters, George Ficher, Neoperl, Lubrizol, Jindal Stainless, Pidilite etc.</p>		<h2>Highlights  <span class="theme_color">of the Event</span></h2>		<ul class="list-style-two">			<li class="ptext">Mahotsav became a record holder in the <strong>Limca Book of Records</strong> for getting the most numbers of plumbers under one roof. </li>			<li class="ptext"><b>Over 12000 Plumbers witnessed</b> the event and got their hands on the latest trends and technology of the Industry.</li>			<li class="ptext">Plumber Konnect was launched in the event which is world’s first app that aims to bring certified plumbers closer to its users.</li>			<li class="ptext">Hon’ble Minister Shri Dharmendra Pradhan observed the importance of events like Mahotsav which serves as a bridge between the industry and plumbers.</li>		</ul>					</div>	<div class="col-sm-4">		<img src="images/modi_letter.png" />	</div></div>				<div class="row">			<div class="gallery-block mix water psm col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">			<div class="inner-box">				<div class="image">					<img src="images/media/370-485/Photo_Gallery/Plumbing Skills Mahotsav/1A1A5159.jpg" alt="" />					<div class="overlay-box">						<div class="overlay-inner">							<h3><a href="#">Plumbing Skills Mahotsav</a></h3>							<ul class="links">								<li><a href="images/media/full_images/Photo_Gallery/Plumbing Skills Mahotsav/1A1A5159.jpg" data-fancybox="gallery" data-caption="" class="icon flaticon-full-screen"></a></li>							</ul>						</div>					