nner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/anant_kumar.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>Anant Kumar Hegde</h5>						<h6>Former Minister of State, Skill Development and Entrepreneurship</h6>											</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">The initiative by the Indian Plumbing Skills Council (WMPSC) to bring over 10,000 plumbers under one roof will provide an excellent opportunity to communicate with all the sub sectors of plumbing industry and inspire them to become a part of Skill India mission envisioned by Hon'ble Prime Minister, Shri Narendra Modi.</div>				</div>			</div>			<div class="testimonial-block-two" style="padding-top: 30px;">				<div class="inner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/dharmendra.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>Dharmendra Pradhan</h5>						<h6>Former Minister of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship</h6>											</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">The 'Plumbing Skill Mahotsav' being organized by Indian Plumbing Skills Council (WMPSC) is a good platform for plumbing community to showcase their achievements and initiatives. It would pave the way for the youth towards nurturing their talent in plumbing workforce and turn that into a meaningful source of livelihood.</div>				</div>			</div>			<div class="testimonial-block-two" style="padding-top: 30px;">				<div class="inner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/manish_kumar.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>Dr. Manish Kumar</h5>						<h6>Managing Director & CEO</h6>						<h6>NSDC</h6>					</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">Given the growing demands of real estate, infrastructure and with it, the need for highly skilled plumbers, I commend the efforts of Indian Plumbing Skills Council (WMPSC) for the efforts they have been making for enhancing the skills of plumbers across the country. I congratulate them for undertaking initiatives such as 'Plumbing Skills Mahotsav' which aims to exhibit the latest of plumbing products and provide networking opportunities to all stakeholders.</div>				</div>			</div>			<div class="testimonial-block-two" style="padding-top: 30px;">				<div class="inner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/thomas.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>Thomas Berheide</h5>						<h6>Managing Director</h6>						<h6>Rothenberger</h6>					</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">At Plumbing Mahotsav, we want to skill the maximum number of people. We applaud WMPSC's initiative to provide India with a strong, competitive and skilled workforce for plumbing. ROTHENBERGER is always ready to support WMPSC by providing trainings and highly Professional Pipe Tools.</div>				</div>			</div>			<div class="testimonial-block-two" style="padding-top: 30px;">				<div class="inner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/bbsingh.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>B.B. Singh</h5>						<h6>BD Head</h6>						<h6>NSF International</h6>					</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">I think MPSC should do such events every year or at least every alternate year. So far the initiatives to skill or educate the plumbers had been very commercial and were done by various manufacturers to promote their own products.</div>				</div>			</div>			<div class="testimonial-block-two" style="padding-top: 30px;">				<div class="inner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/bantwal.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>Bantwal Ramesh Baliga</h5>						<h6>CEO</h6>						<h6>Watertec</h6>					</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">The Plumbing Mahotsav 2019 would be an ideal platform to implement the company's vision and mission of training and be a part of plumbing members across the country. It’s a great opportunity for Watertec to be a part of the plumbing activities in the country, understand the working of the plumbers and contribute to their growth.</div>				</div>			</div>			<div class="testimonial-block-two" style="padding-top: 30px;">				<div class="inner-box">					<div class="quote-icon flaticon-two-quotes"></div>					<div class="image-outer">						<div class="image">							<img src="images/deepak.jpg" alt="" />						</div>						<h5>Deepak Mehrotra</h5>						<h6>Managing Director</h6>						<h6>Ashirvad Pipes Pvt. Ltd.</h6>					</div>					<div class="text example-1 scrollbar-ripe-malinka">Plumbing Skills Mahotsav 2019 will be a key platform for the entire plumbing industry to meet, brainstorm and demonstrate safe and innovative plumbing skills. WMPSC can do regular events on latest plumbing products and technologies. Also, WMPSC can have dedicated career opportunity zones for plumbers along with career counselling.</div>				</div>			</div>		</div><div class="separator"><span>Mahotsav 2016</span></div>		<h2>Plumbing <span class="theme_color">Skills Mela 2016</span></h2>			<p class="ptext">On 22nd October 2016, Indian Plumbing Skills Council hosted India’s Largest Plumbing Skills Mela at NSIC complex in Okhla, New Delhi. Hon’ble Minister Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy was invited as the Chief Guest at the event. The event saw active participation from 16 organisations from the plumbing and related sectors as sponsors of the event. Over 1300 plumbers visited the event and witnessed the latest technologies and product being used in the industry. WMPSC also felicitated 750 Plumbers with Govt of India and WMPSC certifications. These plumbers went through recognition of prior learning (RPL) from the 5th till the 20th October.</p> <p class="ptext">Hon’ble minister was impressed with the efforts of the team and governing body members of WMPSC and congratulated us on hosting such a grand event. He has also expressed that he would like to see 25,000 plumbers for the next event and promised that he would personally invite Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi for the same. </p> <p class="ptext">Mr SG Deolalikar was also invited as the Guest of honour, and was highly impressed to see the grandeur of the event.he also congratulated Mr RK Somany in putting up such a wonderful show and quoted <strong>”In a career of over six decades, I have never seen so many plumbers at a time under one roof”.</strong></p>		<h2>Highlights  <span class="theme_color">of the Event</span></h2>		<ul class="list-style-two">			<li class="ptext">Over 1300 Plumbers witnessing the latest plumbing products and technologies under one roof.</li>			<li class="ptext">750 plumbers felicitated with Govt. of India & WMPSC Certification.</li>			<li class="ptext">Industry came together to support the cause, as sponsors and got immense mileage.</li>			<li class="ptext">Hon’ble Minister Shri Rajiv Pratap Rudy was flabbergasted with the turn up of plumbers.</li>		</ul>					</div>				</div>											</div>		</div>	</section>    <!--Newsleter Section-->    <?php include "includes/newsletter.php"; ?>    <!--End Newsleter Section-->	<?php include "includes/footer.php"; ?></body></html>